  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0db6\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1 \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"There is no medicine. Be careful.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Government Medical Officers' Association (GMOA) says that due to the shortage of medicines and transportation difficulties, people should be very careful during this time.",
        "Dr. Prasanna Colombage, Member of the Media Committee of the Government Medical Officers' Association (GMOA) said that the stock of drugs in the country is not sufficient at this time and the stock of drugs available is declining and therefore it is important to be as safe as possible at this time.",
        "The doctor also said that in case of an accident during work, housework, etc., it would be difficult to provide transport facilities for the patient as well as for the doctors and other hospital staff.",
        "He was speaking at a media briefing held at the Government Medical Officers' Association office today (27).",
        "He also said that it is very important for people suffering from various diseases to take care of their medicines and take good care of their children at this time."
      ],
